- Install drive
- Partition drive
    mkfs -t ext4 /dev/<sdx>
- Mount drive
    mkdir /mnt/<sdx>
    mount -t auto /dev/<sdx> /mnt/<sdx>
- Set up automount
    ls -al /dev/disk/by-uuid/ # Get UUID
    sudo vim /etc/fstab
- Create new pv and pvc for new drive
- Add pv to charts that require it
